OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FIt's been 12 months since refuse
OL,7,Fworkers in Birmingham downed tools
OL,8,Findefinitely, kicking off what has
OL,9,Fbecome one of the longest industrial
OL,10,Fdisputes in recent memory.
OL,12,FWhat started as a stand against
OL,13,Fchanges to job roles and feared pay
OL,14,Fcuts has turned into a stalemate that
OL,15,Fshows little sign of easing.
OL,17,FBack in early January 2025, refuse
OL,18,Fteams began with short walkouts over
OL,19,Fthe proposed scrapping of the Waste
OL,20,FRecycling and Collection Officer
OL,21,F(WRCO) role.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773302722
OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FBy 11 March, the action had escalated
OL,7,Finto an indefinite all-out strike.
OL,9,FPicket lines formed daily, depots were
OL,10,Fblocked, residents were frustrated,
OL,11,Fand mountains of uncollected rubbish
OL,12,Fpiled up.
OL,14,FThe council then decided to withdraw
OL,15,Fthe Grade 4 Driver/Team Leader role as
OL,16,Fwell, fuelling further anger.
OL,18,FWhere things stand now
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773302722
OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FA year on, the dispute is very much
OL,7,Falive and kicking, with neither side
OL,8,Fready to call it a day.
OL,10,FBirmingham City Council says all 170
OL,11,Fformer WRCOs have been "redeployed" to
OL,12,Fother roles or taken voluntary
OL,13,Fredundancy.
OL,26,@sD@XOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773302722
OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FOf the 144 Grade 4 Driver/Team
OL,7,FLeaders, the majority have accepted
OL,8,Fthe new Grade 3 role six months' pay
OL,9,Fprotection, while others have opted
OL,10,Ffor voluntary redundancy or
OL,11,Falternative roles within the service.
OL,12,FThree were made compulsory redundant
OL,13,Fafter refusing the council's offers.
OL,15,FUnite the Union, meanwhile, hasn't
OL,16,Fbudged on its demand for a fair deal,
OL,17,Finsisting the council's changes have
OL,18,Fslashed incomes for dozens of workers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773302722
OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FNo talks have taken place since the
OL,7,Fcouncil walked out of negotiations
OL,8,Fwith ACAS last summer.
OL,10,FBehind the headlines, tensions have
OL,11,Fonly deepened. Placards were put up
OL,12,Fand ripped down, by the cabinet member
OL,13,Fresponsible for bins, while the
OL,14,Fcouncil also won court injunctions
OL,15,Fbanning people from disrupting agency
OL,16,Fworkers carrying out limited
OL,17,Fcollections.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
