PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773302722
OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FThe human cost has been stark. Before
OL,7,FChristmas, the city saw its first bin
OL,8,Fdriver dismissed, marking the end of a
OL,9,Flong fight for him and two colleagues.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, some agency staff walked
OL,12,Fout after reporting bullying and
OL,13,Fthreats, and leaked videos revealed
OL,14,Fmanagers warning striking agency
OL,15,Fworkers they wouldn't secure permanent
OL,16,Fjobs if they stayed out.
OL,18,FNeither side is giving way, resulting
OL,19,Fin a toxic political and civic
OL,20,Fheadache that has stretched across all
OL,21,Ffour seasons.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773302722
OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FThe real impact
OL,8,FAsk residents around Birmingham and
OL,9,Fthe mood varies wildly. In some
OL,10,Fneighbourhoods, piles of rubbish
OL,11,Fbecame part of the street scene early
OL,12,Fon, drawing complaints about vermin
OL,13,Fand blocked bins.
OL,15,FMore recent efforts have cleared much
OL,16,Fof the worst, but the smell of
OL,17,Ffrustration lingers as much as the
OL,18,Flingering scent by some alleyways.
OL,20,FFor households juggling everyday life,
OL,21,Fit's been galling.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773302722
OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FResidents say they've had enough of
OL,7,Fdisputes that feel remote, with missed
OL,8,Fbin collections, overflowing bins, and
OL,9,Ffly-tipping becoming a symptom of a
OL,10,Fbigger breakdown in local services.
OL,12,FWhat happens next?
OL,14,FA year in, both workers and the
OL,15,Fcouncil are still talking - but just
OL,16,Fnot to each other.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773302722
OL,3,COne year of Birmingham's all-out bin
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FWorkers continue chanting at picket
OL,7,Flines and holding demonstrations
OL,8,Foutside the council house, while
OL,9,Fcouncillors continue promoting a
OL,10,Freformed waste service with separate
OL,11,Frecycling bins and, for the first
OL,12,Ftime, food waste collections.
OL,14,FThe council is waiting for everyone to
OL,15,Ffold - either accept the new roles or
OL,16,Fquit. It insists its changes will
OL,17,Fhappen with or without striking
OL,18,Fworkers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
